{"tid":1306250,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(小心) 香港抗爭者若大失民意，「送中條例」會即時通過","createTime":"2019-07-11T05:43:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T17:06:29.000Z","uid":134071,"like":54,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"bac68c515c41cc51d2dc505ab2e2b7cd90b01f78","tid":1306250,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:43:56.000Z","msg":"抗爭者若失民意， 政府會立即力推惡法！ 係法國已經係咁。<br />\n<br />\n法國總統馬克龍當初強推經濟改革方案， 引發黃背心革命， 馬克龍都要暫撒經濟改革。<br />\n<br />\n但最後，黃背心革命由贏變輸，抗爭者內訌，選舉慘敗。<br />\n上個月，馬克龍見到黃背心敗局已定， 即時再度力推極受爭議既經濟改革方案。  但即使馬克龍再推經濟改革方案，黃背心示威人數也再沒有明顯增加。<br />\n<br />\n民主國家都可以咁玩， 林鄭都可以咁玩。<br />\n只要當香港抗爭者大失民意，林鄭條仆街好可能會即時再推「送中條例」， 而且一星期內就可以通過。（因  「送中條例」目前只係暫緩；如果政府再推， 最快一星期就可以過到。）<br />\n所以， 香港抗爭者一定要keep住民意， 唔可以比林鄭偷到雞。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"365681b06bd3d4a00b353da35cb5d12492d70d64","tid":1306250,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:44:28.000Z","msg":"補充<br />\n<br />\n(法國) 黃背心運動由贏變輸，抗爭者內訌，選舉慘敗<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1306103/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1306103/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"e49eb8fab5441f84da035ee251303ea93aa388f0","tid":1306250,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:45:55.000Z","msg":"小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b5e9aa2cc15d54265d2fd3150816cb1ca99a195","tid":1306250,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:49:00.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"6012552616941784dccaefea62ad82a0200428f0","tid":1306250,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:54:50.000Z","msg":"小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be14cce81dcf8a6a2f27adda8d79abbd4e961f63","tid":1306250,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r